pageContext.claim: “I'm watching those doors -- not one person's left. … So if you hear tomorrow when they read, ‘People left.’ Nobody left early. There hasn't been one person, this long. But when you read it you just say fake news.”
pageContext.analysis: False. The White House pool report said: "POTUS’s CPAC speech concluded at 2:18pm. He spoke for just over two hours. Members of the audience left early."
